*&quot;Madonna and Child with a member of the Hillensberger family&quot; (Lowe Art Museum, University of Miami, Coral Gables, Florida)
*&quot;Our Lady of the Seven Sorrows&quot; (Church of Our Lady, Bruges) (c. 1518)
